cmake -DCMAKE_INSTALL_PREFIX=/amssw/duranti/geant4.11.00-install -DGEANT4_USE_GDML=ON -DGEANT4_BUILD_MULTITHREADED=ON  -DGEANT4_INSTALL_DATA=ON -DGEANT4_INSTALL_DATADIR=/amssw/duranti/geant4-share -DCMAKE_CXX_STANDARD=17 -DGEANT4_USE_QT=ON ../geant4.11.00.p02

e poi, ovviamente:

make -j8
make install
